      <category domain="https://blog.messywind.top/categories/%E6%9D%82%E9%A1%B9/">杂项</category>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.messywind.top/image/12.png&#34; alt=&#34;/image/12.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://blog.messywind.top/image/12.png?size=small, https://blog.messywind.top/image/12.png?size=medium 1.5x, https://blog.messywind.top/image/12.png?size=large 2x&#34; data-title=&#34;/image/12.png&#34; style=&#34;background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;&#34; onload=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded=&#39;&#39;;&#34; onerror=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.removeAttribute(i);}&#34;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A 选项： $n=1$ 时， $p_1=1$，$∴ H(X)=−p_1\log_2p_1=0$，正确。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;B 选项： $n=2$ 时， $p_1+p_2=1$，$H(X)=-(p_{1}\log_{2}p_{1}+p_{2}\log_{2}p_{2})=-[p_{1}\log_{2}p_{1}+(1-p_{1})\log_{2}(1-p_{1})]$&lt;/p&gt;</description>
