      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.messywind.top/image/pi.png&#34; alt=&#34;2&#34; srcset=&#34;https://blog.messywind.top/image/pi.png?size=small, https://blog.messywind.top/image/pi.png?size=medium 1.5x, https://blog.messywind.top/image/pi.png?size=large 2x&#34; data-title=&#34;2&#34; style=&#34;background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;&#34; onload=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded=&#39;&#39;;&#34; onerror=&#34;this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of [&#39;style&#39;, &#39;data-title&#39;,&#39;onerror&#39;,&#39;onload&#39;]){this.removeAttribute(i);}&#34;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;分析：&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$(1)$ $g&#39;(x)=\dfrac{π^{x}}{x^{π}}(\lnπ-\frac{π}{x})$&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$∴g&#39;(1)=π(\lnπ-π)$&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$(2)$ $f(x)=\int x \text{d} \frac{π^{x}}{\lnπ} = \dfrac{xπ^{x}}{\lnπ}-\int \dfrac{π^{x}}{\lnπ}\text{d}x = \dfrac{xπ^{x}}{\lnπ}-\dfrac{π^{x}}{\ln ^ 2π}$&lt;/p&gt;</description>
